        <p>John Hosking was born in 1952 and studied one year Foundation, three years Fine Art at Epsom School of Art and Design and three years P/T MA Fine Art at Canterbury KIAD.</p>
        <p>John's work is in public and private collections including the Metropole Arts Centre Permanent Collection, Hampshire County Council, The Department of the Enviroment and Imperial  College, London.</p>
